dct_title_s: Cambridge Shire and Isle of Ely
dct_description_sm: DaLatitudinal and longitudinal lines along left and bottom margins.
Shows boundaries, topography, vegetation, rivers, drainage canals, roads and settlements.
Appears in abridgement of Camden's Britannia, printed by John Bill, 1626.
